Modal Dialog

Authors: Samuel Cole <sam@samuelcole.name>, Adam Hooper <adam@adamhooper.com>

DESCRIPTION

All the rails helpers, sass, haml layouts, and javascript you would ever want to build a sweet modal dialog.

